[!--
NOTICE TO TRANSLATORS

To generate a list of links to all pages that SCP-3939 uses, please paste the following into any page on the wiki:

[[module ListPages category="fragment" parent="scp-3939" order="created_at" perPage="250"]]
%%title_linked%%
[[/module]]

A spreadsheet is available which contains the entire story in a format which may be better for your needs. Please contact me (Croquembouche) if you need it.

When re-creating this SCP, for example for translation purposes, it is of utmost importance that the pages are created in the right order - starting with number 0, and ending with number 66.

Thank you.

SCP-3939 begins below.
--]

[[module CSS]]
:root { --swatch-primary: 187, 0, 17; }
.story {
  clear: both; border: 3px black solid; padding: calc(20px - 1em) 0 20px 0;
}
.story p {
  margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; 
}
.choices {
  clear: both;
}
.choices a {
  height: 30px; border: 1px solid #b01; border-right: 1px solid transparent; line-height: 30px; position: relative; background: white; z-index: 8; margin-bottom: 0.5em; float: left; clear: both; padding-left: 7px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px
}
.choices a::before {
  content: ""; position: absolute; border: 16px solid transparent; border-left: 16px solid #b01; right: -33px; top: -1px; z-index: 6;
}
.choices a::after {
  content: ""; position: absolute; border: 15px solid transparent; border-left: 15px solid white; right: -31px; top: 0; z-index: 7;
}
.choices p {
  clear: both; height: 30px; margin: 0 0 0 0;
}
.footer-wikiwalk-nav {
  margin-top: 50px;
}
span, a {
  word-break: normal !important;
}
@media (max-width: 580px) {
  .choices a {
    line-height: initial !important; margin-left: 10px !important; margin-right: 30px !important;
  }
}
[[/module]]

[[include :scp-wiki-cn:credit:start-standalone]]
**文章：** SCP-3939 (//[编号保留，以待研究员]//)

**作者：** [[*user Croquembouche]]

**致谢：** [[*user Baseplate-Actual]]，[[*user taylor_itkin]]，[[*user Tanhony]]，[[*user MayD]]

这是一篇多选择故事。每一页底部的箭头形状的链接选项表示其可将您带到另一页中。完整阅读一整条这篇SCP的故事线将花费大约15分钟。并不期望您会再读一遍。

[[[cone|作者页]]]
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:credit:end-standalone]]

